OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA partly
OL,6,Fcloudy and mostly dry period, an
OL,7,Fisolated light shower is still
OL,8,Fpossible initially, but these are
OL,9,Flikely to be mainly restricted to the
OL,10,Fcoast overnight. Patchy low cloud and
OL,11,Fmist may form by dawn. Light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAny low cloud or mist will
OL,14,Fclear to leave plenty of fine weather
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells. However, there is
OL,16,Fpotential for an isolated shower to
OL,17,Fdevelop in places. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
