OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FThe
OL,6,Fweather should remain fine on Friday
OL,7,Fwith further spells of warm sunshine.
OL,8,FHowever, the weekend looks slightly
OL,9,Fcooler and more breezy with the chance
OL,10,Fof some rain at times.
